Package: grandtab
Type: Package
Title: Programmatic Access to California GrandTab Chinook Salmon Escapement Data
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Danny", "O'Donnell", email = "dodonnell2011@gmail.com",
    role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides functions to query and retrieve California Department of
    Fish and Wildlife GrandTab Chinook salmon escapement data for all four
    Central Valley runs (fall, late-fall, winter, spring). Supports filtering
    by run type, river system, location, fall run geographic section, and year.
    Includes column metadata lookup, raw table access, table footnotes,
    supplementary winter run data, GrandTab documentation, and an interactive
    map of monitoring locations.
Depends:
    R (>= 4.1.0)
